OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FDowning Street has said it is "very
OL,8,Fconcerning" that an American fighter
OL,9,Fpilot was able to avoid a trial under
OL,10,FEnglish law for strangling a woman in
OL,11,FCambridge.
OL,13,FCaptain Jacob Wulfson was tried at a
OL,14,Fcourt martial on a US airbase despite
OL,15,Fhis alleged crime taking place in the
OL,16,FUK, while he was off-duty.
OL,18,FThe case, which was first reported by
OL,19,Fthe Guardian, was not investigated by
OL,20,Fthe local police and instead handed to
OL,21,Fthe US military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FMr Wulfson's victim, Sarah Steele,
OL,8,Ftold the Guardian she was treated
OL,9,F"incredibly aggressively" by the
OL,10,Fpilot's defence team and felt like she
OL,11,Fwas the one on trial.
OL,13,FThe prime minister's official
OL,14,Fspokesperson questioned why the case
OL,15,Fnever reached the CPS (Crown
OL,16,FProsecution Service).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FNo 10 said: "This is clearly a deeply
OL,8,Fdistressing case, our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith the victim. She's shown
OL,10,Fincredible bravery not only in her
OL,11,Finitial report to police, but also in
OL,12,Fcoming forward to speak to the media
OL,13,Fto help get justice for others."
OL,15,FThe government has confirmed it is
OL,16,F"going to look really carefully at
OL,17,Fwhat's happened here, and we must
OL,18,Fstress that we're still establishing
OL,19,Fthe facts".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"But of course, this is very
OL,8,Fconcerning that a case like this never
OL,9,Freached the CPS, but was investigated
OL,10,Fby US airbase police and heard in
OL,11,Ffront of an all-male panel of air
OL,12,Fforce officers."
OL,14,FOn Friday morning, Justice Minister
OL,15,FJake Richards described the case as
OL,16,F"really serious" and said there are
OL,17,F"issues" around the military courts
OL,18,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FHe raised concerns about military
OL,8,Fcourts and their relation "with our
OL,9,Fcriminal courts and our civil courts".
OL,11,FMs Steele, an academic, met Cpt
OL,12,FWulfson on a dating app and eventually
OL,13,Farranged to meet at his flat while he
OL,14,Fwas working at RAF Lakenheath in
OL,15,FSuffolk.
OL,17,FShe left his flat the next morning
OL,18,Ffeeling that something was wrong,
OL,19,Flater accusing him of non-consensual
OL,20,Fsex, drugging and strangling her, the
OL,21,FGuardian reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FHe was charged with sexual assault and
OL,8,Faggravated sexual contact, and was
OL,9,Fultimately found guilty of
OL,10,Fstrangulation, but acquitted of the
OL,11,Fother charges.
OL,13,FThe judge in the court martial was a
OL,14,FUS Air Force colonel, and the jury was
OL,15,Fa panel of eight all-male Air Force
OL,16,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FSome British terms had to be explained
OL,8,Fto the panel, and Cpt Wulfson's
OL,9,F"enemies killed in action count" as an
OL,10,FF-35 pilot was used as mitigation for
OL,11,Fhis sentence, the newspaper said.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
