PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FSpeaking about the trial, Ms Steele
OL,8,Fsaid: "It was a very difficult system
OL,9,Fto be in, and at times I was treated
OL,10,Fincredibly aggressively, and I felt
OL,11,Flike I was on trial, and it became a
OL,12,Fcharacter assassination.
OL,14,F"People are attacking you with
OL,15,Fassertions that are trying to
OL,16,Fundermine, say that you're lying, say
OL,17,Fthat you're a problem, say that you're
OL,18,Fall manner of evil things, and that
OL,19,Fyou're creating this, and you've got
OL,20,Fto wade through that staring in the
OL,21,Fface of the accused."
OL,26,@}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FMs Steele's case would likely have
OL,8,Fbeen tried at a crown court had it
OL,9,Fbeen handled by the CPS.
OL,11,FThe court martial handed Cpt Wulfson a
OL,12,Fsentence of six months at a
OL,13,Fcorrectional facility at RAF
OL,14,FLakenheath.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782521274
OL,3,CDowning Street concerned after US
OL,4,Cpilot avoids UK trial for strangling
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FCalling for clearer guidance on who
OL,8,Fshould prosecute such cases, she said:
OL,9,F"I think it's really important that
OL,10,Ffor the interests of justice and for
OL,11,Fthe rights of victims, that we have
OL,12,Fclear framework discussion around
OL,13,Fthis."
OL,15,FThere are around 12 active US Air
OL,16,FForce bases across the UK.
OL,18,FThe US military justice system has a
OL,19,Fdistinct legal framework and is
OL,20,Fseparate from British civilian courts.
OL,26,@uD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
